item.title: I have 100 errors!
item.dc:creator: @Project_Realm Project Realm
item.description:
@Project_Realm wrote:

The dreaded 100 error compilation report!

Pretty much, you forgot to add either a semi-colon or a bracket somewhere in the file. Look around the location where you originally added the command for the problem. It’s impossible for anyone to tell where it is, though, just based on the report, since a missing bracket will affect the rest of the .java file.
